details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: What does the road ahead look like?

details.name: Scout
details.text: Amber Noon has a lot of Factories here, Sir.

details.name: Scout
details.text: There is one nearby, with some tanks ready to go.

details.name: Scout
details.text: Main forces are stationed in a nearby town.

details.name: Scout
details.text: They have a number of Towers in the area for support, we should expect a lot of Tanks being produced.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: We need to hasten our work on the Airfield then.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: It is still being worked on, it will take some time for it to provide air support.

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: These veteran units will help in stopping Amber Noon for now, but we can't hold this position for long.
Defend until your Airfield becomes available.

details.name: Airfield crew
details.text: Air support ready to go. Those Tanks are going to be helpless agains them!

details.name: Noble Sidney
details.text: Town guards have been defeated. With an Airfield in this area, Ruby Dusk is able to bring in all the units that we need to beat Amber Noon once and for all.
